{"tid":1397356,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"敘利亞難民於德國街頭當街以武士刀斬殺室友","createTime":"2019-08-02T12:16:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T13:05:52.000Z","uid":133680,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7110c55b0f264a1cc2a1be777a5263d34bd25c3d","tid":1397356,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:16:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190802/mobile/bkn-20190802165107834-0802_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190802%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190802165107834-0802_00912_001.html&d=7O3ztiABqAoAY%2BrF22wgzXNo2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=0e69e9c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190802/mobile/bkn-20190802165107834-0802_00912_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n德國斯圖加特一名敍利亞難民，周三（7月31日）涉在光天化日的大街上，用武士刀殺死前室友，砍下死者手臂後逃去。兇殺過程被目擊者拍下並上載社交網，引起社會震驚。警方已拘捕疑犯，正調查其動機。 <br />\n<br />\n28歲疑兇在2015年難民潮期間抵達德國，曾與36歲的哈薩克裔死者同住。事發當日傍晚，兩人在街上疑發生衝突，其後疑兇突然情緒激動，高舉武士刀多次插向死者頭部，不斷大聲質問他：「為什麼要這樣做？﹗」死者中多刀，當場死亡。 <br />\n<br />\n附近民眾嚇得高聲尖叫四散，亦有市民見狀報案。部份勇敢市民試圖上前阻止，遭疑兇威嚇及喝退。疑兇其後砍下死者手臂，並乘單車逃去。警方到場後派出直升機搜索，成功拘捕疑兇。"},{"pid":"327717ee5d4fa9245690a0d57341b5f9ba344ec9","tid":1397356,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T12:59:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0e10b78609ab3864fd7669d34456fe5eba5db0","tid":1397356,"uid":261505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:04:20.000Z","msg":"大愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3286cc56f3d4aeb76d4648da5409dbfd78e09af9","tid":1397356,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T13:05:52.000Z","msg":"係愛呀 左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}